section.container
	.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-1
		h1.display-1 #0 Installation
		hr
		p Sally.js is an angular.js module. Once you install the package, you need to install angular.js and jquery. After installation, inject sally.js module to your main angularJS module. Check the following. The easiest way of dowloading and installing Sally is to use
			a(href='http://bower.io/' target='_blank')  Bower Package Manager.
		.bumper
		pre
			code //Install prerequsite packages.
			br
			| bower install jquery --save // Install jquery
			| bower install angular --save // Install angular.js
			| bower install sally --save // Install sally.js
			.bumper
			| //In your main module ngApp.js
			| var app = angular.module('YourMainModule', ['sally']);
			| ... 
			| ... 
			| ... 
			.bumper
			| //In your html file...
			| &lt;html ng-app='YourMainModule'>
			| ...
			| ...
			| ...
